                  "content": "Companies started offering health care to its employees during World War I."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "Labor unions never asked for national health care."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "Our culture has long stressed individual responsibility and self-reliance."
                },
